  <h1 class="gem-c-title__text gem-c-title__text--long">
    Making and registering an LPA during the coronavirus outbreak
  </h1>
</div>
  </div>
    <div class="govuk-grid-column-one-third">
      <nav role="navigation" class="gem-c-translation-nav gem-c-translation-nav " aria-label="Translations">
    <ul class="gem-c-translation-nav__list">
        <li class="gem-c-translation-nav__list-item">
            <span lang="en">English</span>
        </li>
        <li class="gem-c-translation-nav__list-item">
            <a hreflang="cy" lang="cy" rel="alternate" class="gem-c-translation-nav__link " href="/guidance/making-and-registering-an-lpa-during-the-coronavirus-outbreak.cy">Cymraeg</a>
        </li>
    </ul>
  </nav>

  </div>

  <div class="govuk-grid-column-two-thirds">
    
  <p class="gem-c-lead-paragraph">If you want to make an LPA now, you can as long as you follow government guidance on social distancing and self-isolating, and observe national restrictions.</p>

  </div>
</div>

